  "texts": [
    "We believe that the structured reasoning approach with high accuracy shows the usefulness of DeepSeek R1 in the healthcare sector.",
    "The sound reasoning combines with an open source model gives a clear path forward for integrating this in the healthcare domain.",
    "Mapping the seven erroneous answers (E1-E7) to their respective clinical domains revealed no consistent clustering of mistakes.",
    "Only seven of the thirty specialties represented in the 100-item set recorded any error, and in five of those the domain contained a single question (Physiology, Neonatology) or two questions (Pharmacology), such that a lone miss reduced accuracy to 0% or 50%.",
    "Among larger categories the system remained highly reliable: Pediatrics 86% (6/7 correct), Surgery 80% (4/5), and Pulmonology 75% (3/4)."
